		\n			<figure><img width=\"539\" height=\"423\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/7015c31c-3a11-45e1-8704-8738a9c5bc4b-1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/7015c31c-3a11-45e1-8704-8738a9c5bc4b-1.png 539w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/7015c31c-3a11-45e1-8704-8738a9c5bc4b-1-300x235.png 300w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure><h3>Customized Service</h3><p>Just tell us your laundry preferences and well return your items exactly as requested! </p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"467\" height=\"361\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/63a383d2-c644-467a-9210-c05adf3b69ef.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/63a383d2-c644-467a-9210-c05adf3b69ef.png 467w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/63a383d2-c644-467a-9210-c05adf3b69ef-300x232.png 300w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure><h3>Support </h3><p>Our support agents are on standby to ensure you\'re laundry needs are met. Contact us through live chat, phone or email. </p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"539\" height=\"423\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/4eb7a8b3-a084-4916-86e8-ac72e1aedbd6.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/4eb7a8b3-a084-4916-86e8-ac72e1aedbd6.png 539w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/4eb7a8b3-a084-4916-86e8-ac72e1aedbd6-300x235.png 300w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure><h3>Easy Ordering</h3><p>Create an account online and doing the laundry will be as easy as ordering a pizza. </p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"482\" height=\"370\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/d6ca9729-54a4-4959-9502-5dccd7820960.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/d6ca9729-54a4-4959-9502-5dccd7820960.png 482w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/d6ca9729-54a4-4959-9502-5dccd7820960-300x230.png 300w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure><h3>Quality Clean </h3><p>From sorting to washing, drying to folding - our laundry pros know how to give your clothes an optimal clean. </p>		\n			<h3>How it Works  </h3>		\n		<p>#1) <b>SIGN-UP:</b> Confirm your pickup address and create your account. <br /><br />#2) <b>SCHEDULE:</b> Make an order and choose a day/time for your pickup &amp; delivery. <br /><br />#3) <b>PICK-UP:</b> Package your dirty laundry in 13 gal size trash bags and give to our driver. <br /><br />#4) <b>DELIVERY:</b> Receive your freshly clean and folded laundry same day, next day or two days.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						View All Locations\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1599\" height=\"1396\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/056cade8-d3ec-429e-8782-3cf3ccb7a85f.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/056cade8-d3ec-429e-8782-3cf3ccb7a85f.png 1599w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/056cade8-d3ec-429e-8782-3cf3ccb7a85f-300x262.png 300w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/056cade8-d3ec-429e-8782-3cf3ccb7a85f-768x670.png 768w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/056cade8-d3ec-429e-8782-3cf3ccb7a85f-1024x894.png 1024w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n										<img width=\"1415\" height=\"976\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/75afbbd5-ba0b-40e8-b110-fa374cf3e50d.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/75afbbd5-ba0b-40e8-b110-fa374cf3e50d.png 1415w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/75afbbd5-ba0b-40e8-b110-fa374cf3e50d-300x207.png 300w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/75afbbd5-ba0b-40e8-b110-fa374cf3e50d-768x530.png 768w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/75afbbd5-ba0b-40e8-b110-fa374cf3e50d-1024x706.png 1024w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n			<h2>Wash & Fold</h2>		\n			<h2>Low, Flat Rate per Bag</h2>		\n		<p>Never guess what your invoice will be with our easy, flat rate pricing. Simply fill up a 13 gal trash bag or one of our reusable bags and we\'ll wash * dry * fold * hang according to your preferences. Kick up your feet and let us do the dirty work.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						View full pricing list\n					</a>\n			<h2>Special Processing</h2>		\n			<h2>Delicate Wash, Air-dry, Stain Treatment and more....</h2>		\n		<p>Do you have a special request for some / all of your order? We\'re happy to oblige! Our laundry pros can provide extra services outside standard wash &amp; fold such as; delicate/hand washing, air drying, and stain treatment. We want to make sure your laundry receives the best care and attention.</p>		\n										<img width=\"525\" height=\"360\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ec8a85a7-c40a-41c3-812d-830c85d30897.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ec8a85a7-c40a-41c3-812d-830c85d30897.png 1000w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ec8a85a7-c40a-41c3-812d-830c85d30897-300x206.png 300w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ec8a85a7-c40a-41c3-812d-830c85d30897-768x526.png 768w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n										<img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/5da2826b-bed7-43ee-9b78-f554ff4719d1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/5da2826b-bed7-43ee-9b78-f554ff4719d1.png 512w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/5da2826b-bed7-43ee-9b78-f554ff4719d1-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/5da2826b-bed7-43ee-9b78-f554ff4719d1-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/5da2826b-bed7-43ee-9b78-f554ff4719d1-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n			<h2>Nationwide Service </h2>		\n			<h2>West Coast to East Coast, we\'ve got you covered. </h2>		\n		<p>We are the nation\'s largest laundry network! Our laundry professionals span from the Pacific shoreline of Seattle to the sandy beaches of Norfolk. We help both household and businesses with their laundry needs. Check to see if Laundry Care is in your neighborhood by entering your address below our FAQs.</p>		\n			<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>		\n												<a href=\"\">How much does it cost?</a>\n					<p>For standard, wash &amp; fold service we charge a flat rate per bag. As much as you can fill! Included with the bag price are items needing special care; hand-wash, air-dry, stain treatment. We&#8217;ll also hang and fold according to your preferences. Ironing is a separate fee of $3 per garment. Items that are not clothing (tablecloths, cleaning rags, etc.) are priced based on the quantity and other processing requirements. Contact our Sales Team for speciality pricing.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">When is my laundry returned? </a>\n					<p>Our standard turnaround is 2 days and is included in our service (no extra fee). If you need it back sooner you can request same day / next day delivery. There is an additional mark up of 30% of your invoice for a faster turnaround.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">How do I find out if you cover my area? </a>\n					<p>On the Home page or the Residential page, enter your address in the &#8220;enter pickup address&#8221; box. We&#8217;ll check to see if our drivers serve your location and let you know right away!</p>\n												<a href=\"\">How do I get started? </a>\n					<p>Setting up laundry service is easy! Once you&#8217;ve created your account, you can request your first pickup!</p>\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						View more FAQs\n					</a>\n			<h1>Get started today!</h1>		\n										<img width=\"525\" height=\"130\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04996d1c-ffdc-443c-8996-e40540ea469c-1024x254.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04996d1c-ffdc-443c-8996-e40540ea469c-1024x254.png 1024w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04996d1c-ffdc-443c-8996-e40540ea469c-300x74.png 300w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04996d1c-ffdc-443c-8996-e40540ea469c-768x190.png 768w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04996d1c-ffdc-443c-8996-e40540ea469c.png 1167w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n											<a href=\"https://www.joinlaundrycare.biz/\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"\">\n							<img width=\"525\" height=\"135\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/66c71e76-f74b-4e74-8b1f-042399003905-1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/66c71e76-f74b-4e74-8b1f-042399003905-1.png 1000w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/66c71e76-f74b-4e74-8b1f-042399003905-1-300x77.png 300w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/66c71e76-f74b-4e74-8b1f-042399003905-1-768x197.png 768w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />								</a>\n		<p>Connect with us on</p>		\n			<a href=\"facebook.com\">\n			</a>\n			<a href=\"twitter.com\">\n			</a>\n			<h2>QUICK LINKS</h2>		\n		<a style=\"color:#ffff\" href=\"https://www.laundrycare.biz/\">Residential</a><br/>\n<a style=\"color:#ffff\"class=\"\" href=\"https://www.laundrycare.biz/commercial\">Commercial</a><br/>\n<a style=\"color:#ffff\"class=\"\" href=\"https://www.laundrycare.biz/locations\">Locations</a><br/>\n<a style=\"color:#ffff\"class=\"\" href=\"https://www.laundrycare.biz/pricing\">Pricing</a><br/>\n<a style=\"color:#ffff\"class=\"\" href=\"https://www.laundrycare.biz/faq\">FAQ</a><br/>\n<a style=\"color:#ffff\"class=\"footer-link\" href=\"https://www.laundrycare.biz/blog\">Blog</a><br/>\n<a style=\"color:#ffff\"class=\"\" href=\"https://www.laundrycare.biz/gift-card\">Gift Card</a><br/>\n<a style=\"color:#ffff\"class=\"\" href=\"https://www.laundrycare.biz/signup\">Signup</a><br/>\n