230.png 300w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure><h3>Quality Clean </h3><p>From sorting to washing, drying to folding - our laundry pros know how to give your clothes an optimal clean. </p>		\n			<h3>How it Works  </h3>		\n		<p>#1) <b>SIGN-UP:</b> Confirm your pickup address and create your account. <br /><br />#2) <b>SCHEDULE:</b> Make an order and choose a day/time for your pickup &amp; delivery. <br /><br />#3) <b>PICK-UP:</b> Package your dirty laundry in 13 gal size trash bags and give to our driver. <br /><br />#4) <b>DELIVERY:</b> Receive your freshly clean and folded laundry same day, next day or two days.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						View All Locations\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1599\" height=\"1396\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/056cade8-d3ec-429e-8782-3cf3ccb7a85f.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/056cade8-d3ec-429e-8782-3cf3ccb7a85f.png 1599w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/056cade8-d3ec-429e-8782-3cf3ccb7a85f-300x262.png 300w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/056cade8-d3ec-429e-8782-3cf3ccb7a85f-768x670.png 768w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/056cade8-d3ec-429e-8782-3cf3ccb7a85f-1024x894.png 1024w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n										<img width=\"1415\" height=\"976\" src=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/75afbbd5-ba0b-40e8-b110-fa374cf3e50d.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/75afbbd5-ba0b-40e8-b110-fa374cf3e50d.png 1415w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/75afbbd5-ba0b-40e8-b110-fa374cf3e50d-300x207.png 300w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/75afbbd5-ba0b-40e8-b110-fa374cf3e50d-768x530.png 768w, http://localhost/laundrycare/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/75afbbd5-ba0b-40e8-b110-fa374cf3e50d-1024x706.png 1024w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n			<h2>Wash & Fold</h2>		\n